data.description: Open House 10/28/23 from 12-3 pm.  Multiple homes available for Open House in Woodcreek on 10/28/23 from 12-3pm.  ***Sellers are motivated and will entertain reasonable offers.***Welcome to your dream home nestled in a serene corner lot that offers unparalleled views of the adjacent golf course. This exquisite 3-bedroom, 3-bathroom residence boasts 1,872 square feet of living space, combining elegance, comfort, and the perfect blend of indoor-outdoor living. Situated in the highly desirable Woodcreek neighborhood, this home offers easy access to the golf course for avid golfers and nature enthusiasts alike. The community is known for its friendly atmosphere and well-maintained properties, making it an ideal place to call home.    Located on a spacious corner lot, this home boasts a striking curb appeal with freshly painted siding and a brand-new metal roof that not only enhances aesthetics but also provides long-lasting durability. Manicured landscaping, two driveways, beautiful mature trees and a charming 16" rock wall with wrought iron fence, adds to the charm of this beautiful property. The backyard is a private oasis, with spacious covered patio that is perfect for outdoor entertaining. Enjoy sipping your favorite beverage in your shaded backyard while watching the deer roam on the adjacent golf greens.    Step inside to discover a bright and airy living area featuring newly painted walls that exude a sense of freshness and modernity, vaulted ceilings and an impressive fireplace.  The kitchen is a chef's delight with custom cabinets including a Lazy Susan and a secret pull out cabinet, sleek countertops, new stainless steel appliances and a wine fridge!    The spacious primary bedroom suite is a tranquil retreat, offering a private en-suite bathroom, with an updated tub/shower with a new sliding glass door, his and hers closets and updated countertops with dual sinks. Two additional well-appointed bedrooms offer plenty of space for family or guests. The secondary master suite is the perfect place for kids, an out-of-town guest or an aging family member or friend.  Take advantage of the additional storage space with the built-in cabinets found in closets and the living room shelving. After a long day golfing, tuck in your golf cart for the night in its own dedicated garage bay.  No need to unload the clubs!    Recent updates to note:  metal roof, window coverings, exterior paint, interior paint, bathroom countertops, grinder pump for septic, garage door, spray-foam attic insulation to the soffits, stainless steel appliances.    With a golf course behind the property and the Young Judea Retreat across the street, the immediate surroundings of this property are likely to remain unchanged for many years to come. Don't miss the opportunity to make this exceptional property your own and experience the perfect blend of comfort, and natural beauty.
